  "title": "1 Year Contract Human Resources Assistant (C&B)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities </strong>          </p><ul><li>Medical insurance enrolment, updates, and terminations.                 </li><li>Draft and issue Letters of Guarantee for employee’s hospital admissions or specialist visits. </li><li>Coordinate with healthcare providers, site administrators and employees to ensure smooth processing of LOGs and successful tagging of LOG to the medical invoice. </li><li>Review, process, and monitor medical invoices for accuracy, and ensuring timely payment. </li><li>Consolidate and maintain records of the director’s medical invoices provided by secretaries.     </li><li>Consolidate salary increment requests</li><li>Prepare and submit monthly salary increment reports for approval. </li><li>Send approved salary increment to payroll team for processing. </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong>                  </p><ul><li>Preferably with at least 1 year of relevant HR administration work experience. </li><li>Proficiency in MS Office (Excel, Word, Outlook) </li><li>Comfortable to commit to 1 year contract role. </li></ul><p><br />Qualified candidates are invited to submit their applications in (MSWord) format to</p><p>to Shaun Quek Yew Meng R1660732</p><p>shaunquek@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA Licence No: 99C4599</p><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</strong></em></p>",
